{"tid":1451573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北角疑似大陸公安濫捕，兼用下體逼壓女社主","createTime":"2019-08-11T19:28:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T09:06:17.000Z","uid":389,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ad43fb45548177ed96d8b5c0d9a920637c751b59","tid":1451573,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:28:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dPfAC30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdPfAC30.jpg&h=fe109f95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n北角城市花園社區主任，獨立身分的仇栩欣，於僑冠大廈直播呼籲街坊注意安全時，有兩名長相疑似大陸公安的驚冒人員使用像膠索帶將之綑綁拘捕，並用下體壓任仇栩欣頭部，以致仇栩欣一度呼吸困難幾近窒息。<br />\n<br />\n現場仇高呼：「路該你唔好用下體對任我個頭」<br />\n警冒人員回應：「唔該你唔好諗得咁污穢得唔得呀」<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">呢批警員明顯受過純潔既愛國思想教育</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"68339b610ac1c048673154d68d8ac801a6ba19d2","tid":1451573,"uid":389,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:29:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QY4arZy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQY4arZy.jpg&h=410ff3df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93aeb5c1a124f92d0eb702f209dac394214fcdfd","tid":1451573,"uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:30:19.000Z","msg":"一批愛國人士今日在北角聚集，多次發生零星衝突。城市花園社區主任仇栩欣今晚在附近拍攝期間，被警方阻止，一名警員表示：「又喺度偷影我哋」，另一名警員隨即出手阻止，並謂「你影嚟做咩呀」，仇栩欣詢問「唔可以影嘢咩，點解唔可以影呀」，其後被警方拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，當時只是叫街坊返屋企，被多名制服按在地上，雙手被綁上索帶，指被警員「壓住喉嚨唞唔到氣」，要求入院睇醫生。"},{"pid":"4a6637d80b22024a0f8682abdb6c3bd9ba993ebe","tid":1451573,"uid":389,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:33:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bOLEkkx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbOLEkkx.jpg&h=b8029ec5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Oi6KNd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Oi6KNd.jpg&h=351ae9b7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i